00:34:50,713 --> 00:34:54,516
like small problems from becoming compound and and turn into a much bigger

647
00:34:54,556 --> 00:34:54,836
problems

648
00:34:55,316 --> 00:34:56,217
uh... richard williams

649
00:34:56,677 --> 00:34:58,959
who is like a master animator he wrote this book

650
00:34:59,420 --> 00:35:00,480
animator survival kit

651
00:35:00,781 --> 00:35:02,122
and talks about the long shortcut

652
00:35:03,183 --> 00:35:07,567
