00:40:35,086 --> 00:40:38,028
but I could figure out in about an hour or two,

758
00:40:38,949 --> 00:40:40,309
is this worth pursuing?

759
00:40:41,865 --> 00:40:43,666
And after about an hour, I discovered that, yes,

760
00:40:43,706 --> 00:40:45,187
despite that extra complexity,

761
00:40:45,868 --> 00:40:48,830
we could get a 3D flag to track with the original 2D flag.

762
00:40:48,970 --> 00:40:50,271
At this point, all the commanders had

