01:00:42,846 --> 01:00:43,307
He was awesome.

1149
01:00:43,327 --> 01:00:44,588
He was my MVP of the week.

1150
01:00:47,215 --> 01:00:50,957
We made a thing that was a force of good in the world.

1151
01:00:52,138 --> 01:00:55,220
And that is my personal best case scenario

1152
01:00:55,601 --> 01:00:57,562
for what defines a successful game.

